Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For me, everything's on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't have anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing but shogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...like shogi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I said I had no reason to fight,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but the truth is,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that a beast lives within me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a rampaging beast that would bite off\Neverything in sight to survive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the battle begins, no matter what,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}its hand reaches out\Ntowards the path of survival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if it means misery for others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what kind of world awaits...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's unfortunate for Mr. Kouda.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And to think his own son\Nwould beat him so easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although maybe he was satisfied after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, that's only if he was his real son.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei Kiriyama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rank C-1, 5th dan. Seventeen years old.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Profession: professional shogi player.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}New Message: 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Inbox\NHinata Kawamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}From: Hinata\NTitle: To Kiriyama\NGood work today!\NWe're having\Ncurry tonight,\Nso come over!!\NWe'll be waiting\NSee you! \(^o^)/\N*Hinata*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Rei is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're tired. Dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, hurry up! I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, did you get ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the Kawamoto Family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a house of three sisters\Nwho live in Sangatsu block.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The oldest sister is Akari, the middle sister\Nis Hina, and the youngest is Momo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mikazuki-Dou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And lastly, the owner of the Mikazuki-Dou\NSweet Shop, is the grandfather Someji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We don't have\Nany special connections or anything,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but still, these sisters\Ninvited someone like me into their house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the same as that time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A senpai shogi player forced me to go with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She found me passed out on the sidewalk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?\NWhere are the people you were with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rokugatsu block.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's near my neighborhood.\NI live in Sangatsu block.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:05:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, you're just skin and bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis will pick up any kind of stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I was surprised\Nwhen she brought a person home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}GONG\NGONG\NWHIRL\NWHIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, he woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want some miso soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was my first time there,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but for some reason,\Nthat old house made me feel nostalgic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was my first time\Nmeeting the three sisters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akari, Hina, and Momo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They told me to "come over anytime,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but did they mean it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, just having a place\Nwhere I was told to "come over"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The words alone made me happy,\Nand my stomach felt full.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That alone felt enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I began living on my own,\Nand started attending high school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I was one year behind,\Nso I couldn't really fit in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a huge rice ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My homeroom teacher, Mr. Hayashida, was a\Nshogi fan, and often worried about my situation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he became a professional during\Nmiddle school and considered a genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here, he's just a 17-year-old\Nwith issues like anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he's thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It still hasn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you're looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Rei Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mr. Rei Kiriyama\NMATCH NOTIFICATION
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.13,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHUB
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put me off like that, Kiriyama!\NWe're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Starting with a guy who always calls me\Nbest friend to rival, Harunobu Nikaidou,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the professional shogi players around me\Nall have a strong uniqueness to them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His name is Issa Matsumoto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His playing style is aggressive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fact, all he does is attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Knock it off, Issa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Smith.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:55.12,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,180 cm\NKendo Club\N(almost never attends)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:55.12,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,181 cm\NVolleyball Club\N(never attends)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems they get along well\Nbecause they're both tall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:07:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}During a match,\Nvarious emotions run towards me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to win. I don't want to lose.\NBut, how do I feel about that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have I changed at all?\NEver since that time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't play like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You came to checkmate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though he was my father's friend,\Nevery time he came over,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would get happy and restless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kouda, sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An emergency came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shogi wasn't my favorite, but it was precious\Ntime that I could spend with my busy father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I did my best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the neighborhood and at school,\NI got bullied a lot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just couldn't seem to make any friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet, the words he said\Nwhile on the other side of the shogi board{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}always made a deep impression on me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was the only person\Noutside of my family who did that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day, my normal life suddenly ended,\Nas if it had been ripped away from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}When I returned from the school trip,\Nmy precious father, mother, and little sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...had become cold, stiff, spotted masses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They said it was an involvement\Nwith a drunken truck driver...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apparently, the three of them\Nwere killed instantly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what will happen to their son.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The younger sister, Kiwako,\Nwill probably take him in, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way that woman would agree to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Poor child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I'll find a good orphanage for Rei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}And then he arrived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...like shogi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was the moment of an agreement.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The god of shogi and I\Nwere bound to each other by an ugly lie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I became the child of a shogi family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Waiting for me at that house of shogi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...were the true children of the family, who also\Naspired to be professional shogi players.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kyouko, the daughter,\Nfour years older than me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Ayumu, the son, a third-grader\Nwho was the same age as me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father loved shogi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good or bad,\Neverything was centered around shogi for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Therefore, those who loved him\Nhad no choice but to get stronger...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Ayumu was the first one\Nto have a breakdown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quitting shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why do I have to quit the federation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't beat Rei,\Nthere's no point in going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, right, Kyouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So in the end,\Nonly someone else's kid made the cut?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's Kiriyama's son, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he went out of his way to raise his\Nrival's child, who then upstaged his own kids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How ironic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The cuckoo lays its eggs\Nin the nests of shrikes or meadow buntings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The hatched chick then tosses the original eggs\Nout of the nest before they're hatched.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this way, it takes over the nest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, that's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're really not going to high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to focus on shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After I become a professional,\NI'll do my best to improve my performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to leave as soon as possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I can become independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before I devour the members of that family...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and Father as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, that dream came true\Nand became reality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought if I could support myself\Nwithout any help,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that would become\Nthe "place where I belong."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, what gives? You better get it together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember, you're the "Future Master."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But in my second year, this year...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I lost two matches in a row for the first time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I understand it in my head,\Nbut why can't I move?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I say I have no reason to win,\Nbut why is it so painful when I lose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm always half-hearted...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...with everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to the shopping area, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought, Rei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...looks glum.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei is always quiet and mature like an adult...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I know he cries sometimes,\Nso I worry about him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So... So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you should come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let's eat dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Gerrg
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.81,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crunch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kawamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so. You became\Na professional shogi player in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Nice to meet you. I'm Yuusuke Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I play baseball and hope to become\Na professional in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kiriyama, after becoming a professional,\Nyou went back to high school a year later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't come back to high school\Nbecause you wanted to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I convey to him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret deciding on the direction\Nof my life so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I wanted memories\Nof not running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only I will know my own memories\Nof "running away" and "slacking off".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd think,\N"But I slacked off that time after all."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't explain it well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you wanted\Nto get rid of things like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It got through.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if you don't mind, let's talk again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can get in touch with me\Nthrough Hina... I mean Ms. Kawamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.53,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nervous\NNervous
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've come here.\NSince second grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}57th NHK Cup (7)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask Mr. Kiriyama something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait a second. If Nikaidou is commentating...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we save this video\Nfor next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black, 6-f-Gold General.\NWhite, 3-d-Bishop+.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-R-Rei! Why are you on TV?\NYou said you're in a shogi club, at school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- Rei, no run away!\N- Momo, you're heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh shoot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap. I didn't know Mr. Kiriyama\Nwas keeping it a secret.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't try to act cool, Kiriyama!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You used to be more careful and single-minded\Nback in the 3rd Dan league!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bravery and recklessness\Nare similar but different!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}You're too close to the camera!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take better care of your shogi,\Nand yourself, Kiriyama!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Wow, that's amazing.\N- They're BFF's after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take better care of yourself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're not doing that,\Nis the reason why you can't progress!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Explode
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The kid's angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time\NI've heard you raise your voice, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is kind of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rei.\NWould you please teach me how to play shogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had no idea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If someone had interest in a world I was in,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't know it would make my stomach\Nfeel fluffy, and happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it'll be okay.\NI hope I can remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Don't worry! It looks difficult,\Nbut it's surprisingly simple to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:33.01,RightSignL2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bododo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.02,DefaultLef2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Hina and Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Drawn and Written by\NHarunobu Nikaidou
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi for Beginners Picture Book
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's look at this picture book together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shiny
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ha-Meow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There's a king, too.\NAll different kinds of kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi is a game in which you use\Neight different types of personality and pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}like this to capture your opponent's king.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:16:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nikaidou... You're amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this feeling I have?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.09,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Answer: Exclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Hina and Momo both had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They even put copies\Nof the picture book on the fridge
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so they can remember the moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about it like that,\Nshogi really is marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been around for hundreds of years,\Nand even now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as long as you have the board\Nand pieces, you can enjoy it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, once you learn how to play,\Nit doesn't matter whether
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're an adult or a child.\NYou can have fun playing earnestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And for your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could I have forgotten?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I'm standing in the world of shogi\Nthat Dad longed for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How? How could I have forgotten that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something so important...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't leave a scar at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotou isn't a sane guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear if Mr. Matsunaga is demoted from C-1,\Nhe'll finally retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought in a situation like this,\Nmaybe you're the type to throw the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're such a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could only think of you as the Grim Reaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come to close the curtain\Non my life as a shogi player.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would at least fight fair and square\Nonce more before fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I don't want to die
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must really love shogi, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder how Kyouko\Nwanted me to handle this match.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without care for my feelings,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she'll tell me about\Nmy next opponent and their family,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as if she thought nothing of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of Mr. Yasui,\Nit seems he's finally getting divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I hate this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:19:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I hear the daughter had one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She said,\N"I want to be with Papa until Christmas."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I can't stand it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}This...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Children have it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, they can't choose their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}The way she speaks,\Nher words sticking to me like glue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}But more than anything...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. But come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it was different for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You chose your own parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}...her words that drip with poison...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You chose somebody else's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}...I hate myself for wanting to hear it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A papa who comes home after winning,\Nor a papa who comes home after losing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which would be more fitting\Nas a final Christmas memory?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Why?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}That easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}You can't let go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Don't give up such precious things so easily!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The match with Mr. Yasui ended all too soon\Nthat late afternoon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want to say I gave up\Nin the middle of the game, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this was our last Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all my matches were over for the year,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I became bedridden with a terrible fever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I curled up in my dimly-lit room,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and December 31st,\Nthe last day of the year, arrived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't. I can't get up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}M-Momo. What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Rei-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it, I knew you had a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay, charge!\N- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Rei's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hina, secure the pillow!\N- Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Uh, Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Fluff
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, get your phone, wallet, and keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay in your pajamas,\Nbut put a coat on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:16.11,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gleam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To the doctor, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if you have the flu,\Nyou'll be quarantined and taken care of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll bring you to our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some tea\Nand then you can go lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Internal Medicine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...let's call your home in Mejiro.\NThey're probably worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm living on my own now.\NSo I think it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On your own, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see your phone, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Charging
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Call Log\NKouda Dad Missed Call\NKouda Dad Missed Call\NKouda Dad Missed Call\NKawamoto Missed Call\NKouda Dad Missed Call\NKouda Dad Missed Call
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say "I'm on my own" when\Nyou have people worried about you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad. It's Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei? It's really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You weren't picking up your phone,\Nso I was about to go over there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you sure you're okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment I heard\Nmy father's voice on the phone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I realized how thoughtless I had been.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From his voice, I could tell\Nthat he was really worried about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm an idiot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My thoughts kept spinning around in my head,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but in the end,\NI had just been thinking about myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get up? Let's eat something\Nand take some medicine again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It used to be even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Zzzzz
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We had three more people then,\Nso it was pretty packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Snore Snore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, it's like we were\Nrunning out of oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three people...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.94,0:23:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, that's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.61,0:23:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.03,0:23:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There must be a reason.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.65,0:23:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody in this house talks about their father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.21,0:23:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.13,0:23:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On an important day like New Year's Eve,\Neven though I'm not part of your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you brought me here and took care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong. I wanted you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Kiriyama. Why are you the one crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.60,0:24:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do I feel so at peace when I'm here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This old house...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}had time, everyone, everything, even me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.37,0:24:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}all gently embraced together,\Nand then dozed away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.21,0:24:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}And then, another day starts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.18,0:24:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}A battle will begin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.39,0:24:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}There was a part of me\Nthat couldn't wait for that to happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.98,0:24:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.98,0:24:45.27,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.69,0:24:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kotatsu's are scary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.52,0:24:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I win two, that's 1.2 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.61,0:24:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get back on track,\Nand connect that with next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.11,0:24:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's about that stalker woman, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.74,0:24:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just... kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.03,0:24:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! What is this feeling?
